#~ "adding values to avoid creating new product variants. To do so, set the "
#~ "attribute's&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Variants Creation Mode&lt;/em&gt; field "
#~ "to&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Never (option)&lt;/em&gt;.\n"
#~ "                &lt;/p&gt;\n"
#~ "                &lt;p&gt;Characteristics&amp;nbsp;with multiple values, "
#~ "such as the number of players, should be added multiple times: one "
#~ "attribute line per value. This ensures a proper display on the products' "
#~ "pages.&lt;/p&gt;\n"
